<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      padding: 30px;
      border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 24px;
    }
    .content {
      background: #f9fafb;
      padding: 30px;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-top: none;
      border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
    }
    .score-box {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .score-current {
      font-size: 48px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #ef4444;
    }
    .score-original {
      color: #6b7280;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
    .decay-indicator {
      display: inline-block;
      background: #fef2f2;
      color: #dc2626;
      padding: 4px 12px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 14px;
      font-weight: 500;
      margin-top: 10px;
    }
    .threshold-alert {
      background: #fefce8;
      border: 1px solid #fde047;
      border-radius: 8px;
      padding: 15px;
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .threshold-alert strong {
      color: #ca8a04;
    }
    .cta-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      color: white;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 12px 30px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-top: 20px;
    }
    .cta-button:hover {
      opacity: 0.9;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      padding-top: 20px;
      border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #6b7280;
      text-align: center;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>⚠️ Score Decay Alert</h1>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= @user.email.split('@').first %>,</p>

    <p>The score for your agent <strong><%= @agent.name %></strong> has decayed below the <strong><%= @threshold %>%</strong> retention threshold.</p>

    <div class="score-box">
      <div class="score-current"><%= @current_score.round(1) %></div>
      <div class="score-original">Original score: <%= @original_score.round(1) %></div>
      <div class="decay-indicator">↓ <%= @decay_percentage %>% decay</div>
    </div>

    <div class="threshold-alert">
      <strong>⚠️ Threshold crossed:</strong> Your agent is now retaining only <strong><%= @retention.round(1) %>%</strong> of its original evaluation score.
    </div>

    <p>Score decay occurs naturally over time as evaluations age. To restore your agent's score to its full potential, consider requesting a new evaluation.</p>

    <p style="text-align: center;">
      <a href="<%= @re_evaluate_url %>" class="cta-button">
        View Agent & Re-evaluate
      </a>
    </p>

    <div class="footer">
      <p>You're receiving this because you own <strong><%= @agent.name %></strong> on evaled.ai.</p>
      <p>© <%= Time.current.year %> evaled.ai - Agent Evaluation Platform</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
